/*------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  Purpose:     
  Parameters:  <none>
  Notes:       
------------------------------------------------------------------------------*/
  DEF VAR ll-choice AS LOG NO-UNDO.
  DEF VAR ll-new-record AS LOG NO-UNDO.
  {&methods/lValidateError.i YES}
